# smutHub — permanent redirects (Cloudflare Workers static assets)
#
# Format: [source] [destination] [code]   — see
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/workers/static-assets/redirects/
# Limits: 2,000 static + 100 dynamic rules. Query strings on the incoming
# request are preserved and re-appended to the destination automatically,
# so /smuthub-app.html?q=Powerless lands on /search?q=Powerless.
#
# The search page was renamed smuthub-app.html -> search.html (serving at
# /search) before launch. These 301s keep every previously-shared link,
# bookmark, and indexed URL working, and tell crawlers the move is permanent
# so ranking signals transfer to the new URL.
/smuthub-app.html  /search  301
/smuthub-app       /search  301
